**Features mapped to your requirements:**
- **Create documents** — `POST /api/documents`, "+ New" in the sidebar.
- **Invite collaborators with view/edit rights** — owner-only `POST /api/documents/:id/collaborators` with `role: view|edit`; revoke via `DELETE`.
